          },
          "_name": "content5",
          "_sourceTheme": "mobirise5",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"content5\" group=\"Content\">\n    <mbr-parameters>\n        <header>Size</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"5\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"5\">\n        <input type=\"range\" name=\"textWidth\" title=\"Width\" min=\"4\" max=\"12\" value=\"10\" step=\"1\">\n        <header>Show/Hide</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showTitle\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Subtitle\" name=\"showSubtitle\" checked>\n        <header>Background</header>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" name=\"bgColor\" value=\"#ffffff\">\n    </mbr-parameters>\n    <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n        <div class=\"row justify-content-center\">\n            <div class=\"col-md-12 col-lg-{{textWidth}}\">\n                <h3 class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style mb-4\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\">\n                    <b>Article Title</b>\n                </h3>\n                <h1 class=\"mbr-section-subtitle mbr-fonts-style mb-4\" mbr-if=\"showSubtitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-subtitle\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-1\">Frequently asked questions</h1>\n                <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\">1. What are NeeDoh® toys?<br>NeeDoh® toys are soft, squishy sensory fidget toys designed for stress relief, relaxation, focus, and fun tactile play for kids and adults.<br><br>2. Are NeeDoh® products safe for children?<br><br>NeeDoh® toys are generally suitable for ages 3 and up. Adult supervision is recommended for younger children during play.<br><br>3. What is inside a NeeDoh® toy?<br><br>NeeDoh® toys are filled with a non-toxic, dough-like compound that gives them their signature soft and stretchy texture.<br><br>4. Can NeeDoh® toys help with stress relief?<br><br>Many people use NeeDoh® toys to relax, reduce stress, improve focus, and enjoy calming sensory stimulation throughout the day.<br><br>5. Do NeeDoh® toys return to their original shape?<br><br>Yes, NeeDoh® toys are designed to stretch, squeeze, and squish while returning to their original shape after use.<br><br>6. How do I clean a NeeDoh® toy?<br><br>Clean your NeeDoh® toy gently with a damp cloth and mild soap. Avoid harsh chemicals, machine washing, or excessive heat.<br><br>7. Are there different NeeDoh® styles and sizes?<br><br>Yes, NeeDoh® offers many styles including classic balls, color-changing designs, ice cube textures, mushroom shapes, mini versions, and extra-large squishy toys.<br><br>8. Are NeeDoh® toys good for sensory play?<br><br>NeeDoh® toys are popular sensory fidget toys thanks to their soft textures, satisfying feel, and calming hands-on experience.<br><br>9. Can adults use NeeDoh® products too?<br><br>Absolutely. NeeDoh® toys are enjoyed by both kids and adults for stress relief, focus, desk play, and relaxation.<br><br>10. Are NeeDoh® toys good as gifts?<br><br>Yes, NeeDoh® toys make fun gifts for birthdays, party favors, classrooms, office desks, sensory kits, and everyday surprises.<br></p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
          "_cid": "vjIPqk4hQQ",
          "_anchor": "content5-1h",
          "_protectedParams": [],
          "_global": false,
          "_once": false,
          "_params": {}
        },
        {
          "alias": false,
          "_styles": {
            "padding-top": "(@paddingTop * 1rem)",
