          "_name": "content5",
          "_sourceTheme": "mobirise5",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"content5\" group=\"Content\">\n    <mbr-parameters>\n        <header>Size</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"5\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"5\">\n        <input type=\"range\" name=\"textWidth\" title=\"Width\" min=\"4\" max=\"12\" value=\"10\" step=\"1\">\n        <header>Show/Hide</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showTitle\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Subtitle\" name=\"showSubtitle\" checked>\n        <header>Background</header>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" name=\"bgColor\" value=\"#ffffff\">\n    </mbr-parameters>\n    <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n        <div class=\"row justify-content-center\">\n            <div class=\"col-md-12 col-lg-{{textWidth}}\">\n                <h3 class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style mb-4\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\">\n                    <b>Article Title</b>\n                </h3>\n                <h4 class=\"mbr-section-subtitle mbr-fonts-style mb-4\" mbr-if=\"showSubtitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-subtitle\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\">Terms and Conditions</h4>\n                <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\">Myneedoh provides product recommendations, reviews, guides, and affiliate links to third-party online marketplaces such as <a href=\"https://www.amazon.com\" class=\"text-primary\">Amazon</a>.&nbsp; By accessing our website and using our services, you acknowledge and accept the following Terms and Conditions.<br><br><b>Changes to Our Terms and Conditions<br></b><br>The Terms and Conditions of myneedoh.com may be updated or modified at any time at our sole discretion. Users may or may not be notified of such changes. Any updates become effective immediately after being published on this website. Continued use of the site means you accept the updated Terms and Conditions.<br><br><b>Minimum Age Requirement<br></b><br>By using this website, you confirm that you are at least 18 years old or have permission from a parent or legal guardian to use this website and its services.<br><br><b>Website Usage Terms<br></b><br>The content published on myneedoh.com, including text, graphics, logos, reviews, and images, is intended for personal and informational use only. You may not copy, reproduce, distribute, republish, or exploit any content from this website without written permission.<br><br><b>Third-Party Purchases<br></b><br>myneedoh.com does not directly sell products or process payments. Purchases made through affiliate links are completed on third-party websites such as Amazon and are governed by the terms and policies of those platforms.<br><br>Any transactions, refunds, warranties, shipping, or customer support related to purchased products are solely between you and the third-party retailer or merchant.<br><br><b>Product Information and Availability<br></b><br>We try our best to provide accurate and updated information regarding products, pricing, ratings, and availability. However, product details may change at any time without notice on third-party retailer websites.<br><br>Myneedoh does not guarantee the accuracy, availability, or completeness of any product information displayed on this website.<br><br><b>Affiliate Disclosure<br></b><br>Some links on myneedoh.com are affiliate links. This means we may earn a commission when users purchase products through these links, at no extra cost to the customer.<br><br><b>External Links<br></b><br>Our website may contain links to third-party websites and services. We are not responsible for the content, policies, practices, or reliability of any external websites linked from myneedoh.com.<br><br><b>Accuracy of Information<br></b><br>Users are responsible for ensuring that any information they provide through contact forms or subscriptions is accurate and up to date.<br><br><b>Website Availability<br></b><br>We strive to keep myneedoh.com available and functioning properly at all times. However, we do not guarantee uninterrupted access to the website and may suspend, modify, or discontinue parts of the service without notice.<br><br><b>Intellectual Property<br></b><br>All NeeDoh® product names, logos, trademarks, product images, and related graphics featured on myneedoh are the property of <a href=\"https://schylling.com/\" class=\"text-primary\">Schylling Toys</a> and their respective owners.<br><br>myneedoh.com is an independent affiliate and informational website and is not officially affiliated with or operated by Schylling Toys.<br><br>Any original website design elements, written content, and custom graphics created specifically for myneedoh.com remain the property of myneedoh.com unless otherwise stated.<br><br><b>Limitation of Liability<br></b><br>myneedoh shall not be held responsible for any damages, losses, or issues arising from the use of this website, third-party purchases, product availability, pricing errors, or reliance on information published on this site.<br><br><br></p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
