        {
          "alias": false,
          "_styles": {
            "padding-top": "(@paddingTop * 1rem)",
            "padding-bottom": "(@paddingBottom * 1rem)",
            "background-color": "@bgColor"
          },
          "_name": "content5",
          "_sourceTheme": "mobirise5",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"content5\" group=\"Content\">\n    <mbr-parameters>\n        <header>Size</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"5\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"5\">\n        <input type=\"range\" name=\"textWidth\" title=\"Width\" min=\"4\" max=\"12\" value=\"10\" step=\"1\">\n        <header>Show/Hide</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showTitle\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Subtitle\" name=\"showSubtitle\" checked>\n        <header>Background</header>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" name=\"bgColor\" value=\"#ffffff\">\n    </mbr-parameters>\n    <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n        <div class=\"row justify-content-center\">\n            <div class=\"col-md-12 col-lg-{{textWidth}}\">\n                <h3 class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style mb-4\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\">\n                    <b>Article Title</b>\n                </h3>\n                <h4 class=\"mbr-section-subtitle mbr-fonts-style mb-4\" mbr-if=\"showSubtitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-subtitle\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\">\n                    About us</h4>\n                <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\">Welcome to myneedoh — your destination for discovering the best NeeDoh® toys, stress balls, sensory products, and squishy fun for kids, teens, and adults.<br><br>Our goal is simple: help visitors find exciting, relaxing, and satisfying NeeDoh products through helpful guides, product recommendations, reviews, and curated collections. Whether you are looking for the latest Super NeeDoh, glow-in-the-dark versions, fun textures, or gift ideas, we aim to make exploring these products easy and enjoyable.<br><br>At myneedoh.com, we are passionate about sensory toys and stress-relief products that bring fun, creativity, and relaxation into everyday life. We continuously update our website with new product discoveries, trending NeeDoh collections, and useful information for families, collectors, and toy lovers.<br><br><b>Affiliate Disclosure<br></b><br>myneedoh participates in affiliate programs, including the <a href=\"https://affiliate-program.amazon.com/\" class=\"text-primary\">Amazon Associates Program</a>. This means some links on our website are affiliate links. If you click a link and make a purchase on <a href=\"https://www.amazon.com\" class=\"text-primary\">Amazon</a> we may earn a small commission at no extra cost to you.<br><br>These commissions help support the website, allowing us to continue creating helpful content, product recommendations, and updates for our visitors.<br><br><b>Independent Website Notice<br></b><br>Myneedoh is an independent informational and affiliate website. We are not owned by or officially affiliated with NeeDoh® or <a href=\"https://schylling.com/\" class=\"text-primary\">Schylling Toys.</a> All trademarks, logos, product names, and product images belong to their respective owners.<br><br><b>Our Mission<br></b><br>We believe sensory toys should be fun, accessible, and easy to discover. Our mission is to help users quickly find the best NeeDoh products online while providing a safe, easy-to-use, and informative browsing experience.<br><br>Thank you for visiting myneedoh.<br></p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
          "_cid": "vjITYB25Um",
          "_protectedParams": [],
          "_global": false,
          "_once": false,
          "_params": {},
          "_anchor": "content5-1k"
        },
        {
          "alias": false,
          "_styles": {
            "padding-top": "(@paddingTop * 1rem)",
            "padding-bottom": "(@paddingBottom * 1rem)",
            "& when (@bg-type = 'image')": {
              "background-image": "url(@bg-value)"
            },
            "& when (@bg-type = 'color')": {
              "background-color": "@bg-value"
            },
            ".row-links": {
              "width": "100%",
              "justify-content": "center"
            },
            ".social-row": {
              "width": "100%",
              "justify-content": "center"
            },
            ".media-container-row": {
              "flex-direction": "column",
              "justify-content": "center",
              "align-items": "center",
              ".foot-menu": {
                "list-style": "none",
